# CW Script Manager (Kernel)

## This Repo
Script generation system for Chatting Wizard. Contains model configs, script generators, XLSX exports, HTML guides, and Smart Messages.

## Repo Ecosystem

| Repo | Purpose | Source of truth for | Never edit here |
|---|---|---|---|
| `CW-ScriptManager` (THIS) | Script generation per model | Model configs, XLSX, HTML guides, Smart Messages | Coaching logic, data pipeline |
| `ChattingWizard-main` | Ops hub: coaching, data pipeline, integrations | Coaching, KPIs, briefings, workflows | Scripts |
| `CW-ChattingSchool` | Training platform for chatters | Curriculum, videos, quizzes | Scripts, coaching |
| `cw-coaching` | Deploy artifact ONLY | Nothing — generated output | Everything |

## How to Operate
- When writing script content: load `script-design-rules.mdc` + `onlyfans-banned-words.mdc`
- When creating Smart Messages: load `smart-messages-quality.mdc` + `fan-psychology.mdc`
- When reading model data from Airtable: load `airtable-schema.mdc`
- Be proactive: if a task can be automated, suggest it
